This is the main directory of the TLUSTY distribution. It contains
five subdirectories:

./tlusty   -  TLUSTY source files, IDL ;program PCONV
./synspec  -  SYNSPEC source files
./pretlus  -  source files for the auxilioaruy program PRETLUS
./data     -  neceassry atomic data
./manuals  -  PDF files for 3 papers with the 3-volume User's guide

The direcftory also contains two shell (bash) script files:

RTlusty   -  script for runnimg TLUSTY
RSynspec  -  script for runnimhg SYNSPEC  
